snippet.title: Virtua Tennis 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the first Trailer on Virtua Tennis 3 released on May, 2006. The game is planned to be available on 2006 for the Play Station 3.
Some possible tennis stars appearing on it are: Andy Roddick, Roger Federer, Rafael Nadal, Sebastien Grosjean, James Blake, Lleyton Hewitt, Tim Henman, Carlos Moya, Mario Ancic and David Nalbandian
